claim.claim-text:
Dendritic cell composition according to any one of the preceding claims, wherein the dendritic cells are mature dendritic cells generated by a method comprising the following steps:
(i) provision of monocytes;
(ii) incubation of the monocytes of step i) with IL-4 and GM-CSF;
(iii) incubation of the monocytes of step ii) with IL-4 and GM-CSF in combination with a maturation cocktail.
